   <narrative xml:lang="EN">An online innovative platform that will allow investors and small enterprises trade receivables through an auction mechanism. This project will ease access to finance for small enterprises, in particular, working capital which is at times difficult to finance at reasonable prices using regular loans.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="ES">Una plataforma innovadora que permite a inversionistas y peque&#xF1;as empresas transar cuentas por cobrar (facturas) v&#xED;a mecanismo de subasta. Este proyecto facilitar&#xE1; acceso a financiamiento para peque&#xF1;as empresas, en particular satisfacer sus necesidades de capital de trabajo con el precio razonable.</narrative>
  </description>
